---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | ZynfexGame" description="About the ZynfexGame team and our mission.">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-12 md:py-20 text-gray-300">
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center font-black text-5xl mb-8 shadow-2xl shadow-indigo-500/20">⚡</div>
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl text-white font-black mb-6 tracking-tight">The ZynfexGame Story</h1>
			<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-indigo-400 font-medium">Redefining Browser Gaming for 2026</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-20">
			<div class="space-y-6">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-white flex items-center gap-3">
					<span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full"></span>
					Our Mission
				</h2>
				<p class="leading-relaxed">
					Founded in early 2026, **ZynfexGame** was born out of a simple frustration: the state of modern web gaming. Most portals are cluttered with intrusive ads, broken links, and poorly optimized games that lag on school or office networks.
				</p>
				<p class="leading-relaxed">
					We set out to build a platform that prioritizes **Speed, Security, and Quality**. Every game on our portal is hand-picked, performance-tested, and optimized to run flawlessly on everything from a high-end gaming PC to a standard school Chromebook.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-[#0f0c24] border border-[#231f47] p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-white flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
					<span class="text-indigo-500">💎</span>
					Our Core Values
				</h2>
				<ul class="space-y-4">
					<li class="flex gap-3">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
						<span><strong>Zero Latency:</strong> Hosted on a global edge network for instant play.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
						<span><strong>Safe & Secure:</strong> No downloads, no track-heavy trackers, pure fun.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
						<span><strong>Universal Access:</strong> Fully unblocked and cross-device compatible.</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="bg-indigo-600/5 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-20 border border-indigo-500/10">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-8 text-center">How We Curate Our Library</h2>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<div class="text-center">
					<div class="text-3xl mb-4">🔍</div>
					<h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">1. Discovery</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">We scan the global indie and IO scenes for high-potential, innovative titles.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="text-center">
					<div class="text-3xl mb-4">🧪</div>
					<h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">2. Testing</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Every game undergoes a 48-hour 'Lag-Stress-Test' on various network conditions.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="text-center">
					<div class="text-3xl mb-4">🚀</div>
					<h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">3. Deployment</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-300">We host and optimize assets locally to ensure lightning-fast load times.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-20">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-6">A Message to Our Community</h2>
			<p class="leading-relaxed mb-8">
				ZynfexGame is more than just a place to play games—it's a community built by gamers for gamers. We believe that entertainment should be free, fast, and accessible to everyone, regardless of where they are or what device they are using.
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
				<a href="mailto:contact@zynfexgame.me" class="bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-2xl transition-all shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 active:scale-95">
					Contact Support
				</a>
				<a href="/" class="bg-[#1b1736] hover:bg-[#25204d] text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-2xl transition-all border border-gray-800 active:scale-95">
					Back to Games
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
